# Covers: Chat, Topic, TellTopic, Display, AddNews, JoinClan, EndChat

Event ChatEvent
  Chat TownSmith
End

Topic TownSmith.Welcome
  Text "Welcome to my shop, traveler!
  TellTopic TownSmith.Services
End

Topic TownSmith.Services
  Display weapons.asc
  AddNews New weapons are available at the smithy!
  JoinClan
  EndChat
End
